                },
                {
                    "stepNo":  "2",
                    "stepDescription": "For seasoning, heat oil in a pan, once heated, add cumin seeds, allow it splutter. Add curry leaves and red chillies. Saute for 5 secs. Add garlic cloves and immediately switch off the stove. Remove the pan from the stove. However, keep stirring the cloves as the oil will be hot. Once oil is little warm, add all dry powders in oil and mix it well.",
